   115‚Üí## API Reference
   117‚Üí### Types
   119‚Üí- `MCPHost` - Main SDK type
   120‚Üí- `Options` - Configuration options
   121‚Üí- `Message` - Conversation message
   122‚Üí- `ToolCall` - Tool invocation details
   123‚Üí
   124‚Üí### Methods
   126‚Üí- `New(ctx, opts)` - Create new MCPHost instance
   127‚Üí- `Prompt(ctx, message)` - Send message and get response
   128‚Üí- `PromptWithCallbacks(ctx, message, ...)` - Send message with progress callbacks
   129‚Üí- `LoadSession(path)` - Load session from file
   130‚Üí- `SaveSession(path)` - Save session to file
   131‚Üí- `ClearSession()` - Clear conversation history
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
   136‚Üí## Environment Variables
   138‚ÜíAll CLI environment variables work with the SDK:
   139‚Üí
   140‚Üí- `MCPHOST_MODEL` - Override model
   141‚Üí- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - Anthropic API key
   142‚Üí- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API key
   143‚Üí- `GEMINI_API_KEY` - Google API key
   144‚Üí- etc.
   145‚Üí
   146‚Üí## License
   148‚ÜíSame as MCPHost CLI

